{"tid":221063,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益，點對付啲閪到震既鄰居/樓上樓下？","createTime":"2017-04-28T12:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T00:36:48.000Z","uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdf805a677de8a8c1202a5e6bd080bffae04ca4","tid":221063,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"好似我樓上果個冚家產咁，<br />\n唔知搞啲咩搞到我浴室附近果個位既天花板滲水，<br />\n有時夜晚又唔知係度做工程定咩 成日都聽到啲搬野聲同鋸野聲<br />\n早排就成袋垃圾扔落黎我果度個晾衫架度<br />\n影哂相投訴完管理處又意見接受，態度照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家就裝修緊係度日鑽夜鑽，有時仲嘭嘭聲咁唔知搞緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多位巴絲有咩對策可以應付依啲撚屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6d36220c952ebd9fa8ce536a84547996f2403d","tid":221063,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfd94e449ccbf68cc3c4dc7322298e1e6284dbd","tid":221063,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"人地裝修就無得屌嘅其實 呢一刻你憎 下一刻係你要裝修你又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0539c43dea1ce4dfdb29db36959f4e7a99e0ea6","tid":221063,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地裝修就無得屌嘅其實 呢一刻你憎 下一刻係你要裝修你又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就要睇下佢幾點鐘。太夜/假日可以投訴"},{"pid":"d655a6a9f6bb891fad444eece159ebbbeb448cc2","tid":221063,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:03:43.000Z","msg":"震樓神器"},{"pid":"9a855b41370f868ad0183d011c08528abfb2ec50","tid":221063,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"煙鏟鄰居先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓下周不時企近窗食 <br />\n凌晨時分飄入屋企人間房 佢哋瞓着咗就全部硬食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚嬲呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bc43a062adb4247015822a175c33b0f6f7be3e","tid":221063,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"我樓上就11點半開始不停有好似著高跟鞋行路嘅聲<br />\n一直到1點幾<br />\n保安講話樓上係隻貓係到玩玩具<br />\n佢都控制唔到<br />\n屌你老母可唔可以去法庭申請禁制令"},{"pid":"2aa6251325534e2746b4c6d6d7fb6accf99ebec5","tid":221063,"uid":66597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我樓上就11點半開始不停有好似著高跟鞋行路嘅聲<br />\n一直到1點幾<br />\n保安講話樓上係隻貓係到玩玩具<br />\n佢都控制唔到<br />\n屌你老母可唔可以去法庭申請禁制令</blockquote><br />\n屌你老未我即刻報警唔撚忍"},{"pid":"f26a65068e2b35b95ac1aeeb61ddc6127219f97b","tid":221063,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>震樓神器</blockquote><br />\n震到樓上樓下仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7528af20860a2eba9937189370f69ea97b61cac3","tid":221063,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:55:58.000Z","msg":"共震器"},{"pid":"b48daebab6afc0252233ce05cf58cfb1dd8002ca","tid":221063,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:08:00.000Z","msg":"樓上噪音反制系統"},{"pid":"11af03a70ffb70afcdb551450219244377ab9846","tid":221063,"uid":8829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:05:40.000Z","msg":"樓上成日亂扔垃圾<br />\n煙頭 杯面蓋 手機殼 用過既紙巾<br />\n但樓上有10層 唔知邊戶<br />\n普通垃圾都算 有次煙頭未熄哂<br />\n個蓬比佢燒左個洞<br />\n有冇方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d42fa8ee2b25b0d494532f825bcde3a4dd52831","tid":221063,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}